data.description: Check out this stunning, open floorplan with 3 spacious bedrooms and a loft. This move-in ready, updated home with vinyl plank throughout the main level, formal dining and casual dining off the updated kitchen, large living room with fireplace, and spacious office on main level. The loft upstairs is great for movie nights and entertaining. Huge fenced in back yard with mature trees, patio, and firepit. Convenient Avon location in Lakeland Farms close to dining, shopping, and schools.
